    Class Description
    VarDataDouble
    This class overrides the Data class and reads the iRacingValue

    VarDataDoubleTape
    This tape reader conditionally returns the tape percentage based on the build if prior to april 22, 2014 the tape was simply values from 0 to 10 after that, 0 - 100.
    VarDataDoubleTape4
    use this class if the tape value returns these 4 possible values, 0,100,200,300,400 it will convert them to percentage.
    VarDataDoubleTapePct
    This tape reader simply divides the value by 100 to normalize it to a percentage
